				"Based on a MOS 1 MHz 6502A^",
"CPU, the Oric-1 came in 16^",
"KB or 48 KB RAM variants^",
"for 129 and 169 GBP^",
"respectively, matching the^",
"models available for the^",
"popular ZX Spectrum and^",
"undercutting the price of^",
"the 48 KB version of the^",
"Spectrum by a few pounds.^",
"The '48 KB' Oric-1 version^",
"was actually 64 KB. The top^",
"16 KB of memory are masked^",
"by the BASIC ROM and thus^",
"normally not available for^",
"the user; The optional disc^",
"drive unit contains some^",
"additional hardware that^",
"allows it to enable or^",
"disable the ROM, effectively^",
"adding 16 KB of RAM to the^",
"machine.^"
